{#- ### Top Mitigations — per-component sub-tables with paragraph divider.

    Layout (2026-05 update — replaces the in-table divider-row form because
    Markdown pipe-tables have no colspan and the `| label | | | | |`
    render produced one cell + 4 visually broken empty cells; per-component
    `####` H4 sub-headers were rejected in a prior iteration as too noisy):

      ↳ <Component Name> (<c-id>) — N item(s)         ← bold paragraph
      | # | Priority | Mitigation | Addresses | Effort |
      |---|---|---|---|---|
      | 1 | P1 | ...                                   ← rows for that bucket
      | 2 | P1 | ...

      ↳ <Next Component> (<c-id>) — M item(s)         ← next paragraph divider
      | # | Priority | Mitigation | Addresses | Effort |
      |---|---|---|---|---|
      | 3 | P1 | ...

    The `↳ … N item(s)` paragraph sits OUTSIDE the table, visually spanning
    the full table width without needing colspan. Each pipe-table has its
    own header so the contract checker (qa_checks.py table_checks) still
    sees the canonical `| # | Priority | Mitigation | Addresses | Effort |`
    header — one occurrence is enough.

    Inputs:
      groups    : list of { header, divider_label, include_affects_column, mitigations[] }
                  - header:        optional `####` sub-header (legacy); usually None
                  - divider_label: paragraph divider text per group (NEW 2026-05)
                  - mitigations[]: data rows with continuous global numbering
                                   { number, id, title, primary_component_id,
                                     addresses[{ref,label}], effort, priority }
                                   Pre-sorted: P1 → P2, severity, effort, ID.
      intro     : top-of-section paragraph string (mentions §9 register)
      footer    : optional italic footer line under the table (may be None)
-#}
### Top Mitigations

{{ intro }}
{% for g in groups %}
{%- if g.header %}
#### {{ g.header }}

{% endif -%}
{%- if g.divider_label %}
**{{ g.divider_label }}**

{% endif -%}
| # | Priority | Mitigation | Addresses | Effort |
|---|---|---|---|---|
{%- for m in g.mitigations %}
| **{{ m.number }}** | **{{ m.priority }}** | [{{ m.id }}](#{{ m.id | lower }}) — {{ m.title }} | {% for a in m.addresses %}[{{ a.ref | replace('T-', 'F-') }}](#{{ (a.ref | replace('T-', 'F-')) | lower }}){% if a.label %} — {{ a.label }}{% endif %}{% if not loop.last %}<br/>{% endif %}{% endfor %} | {{ m.effort }} |
{%- endfor %}
{% endfor -%}
{%- if footer %}

{{ footer }}
{% endif %}
